{"tid":1638392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒 : 海怡對出發現黑衣浮屍","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T07:28:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"aa40a8ef529783451c25b5091211ffdcafc7f353","tid":1638392,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"【海怡出現浮屍】<br />\n<br />\n剛有街坊在海怡對開海面發現身穿黑衣的浮屍，我隨即趕往現場，目睹消防及警隊的處理經過。<br />\n<br />\n居住本區十多年，從未聽聞同類事情，情況實在相當特殊和嚴重，尤其是街坊人心惶惶，更希望了解如此情況發生的來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n我已聯絡海怡管理處，盼望了解海濱長廊有否任何閉路電視的錄影片段，如有任何最新消息，將跟大家匯報。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2519062828186210?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2519062828186210%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6ce99ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2519062828186210?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"eee9f5d8670aba5ca18d50b8101a18b895f694b8","tid":1638392,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99ace1bf9caa3f2b26e9056b9c4a60d96fa6c59","tid":1638392,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb2754d0925a7edbfee717e672c29aed82d2a0e","tid":1638392,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"一定係女性啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n